{
  "name": "Hagai",
  "chapters": [
    {
      "name": "Hagai 1",
      "chapter": 1,
      "link": "https://biblia.resursecrestine.ro/hagai",
      "verses": [
        {
          "type": "title",
          "text": "HAGAI SAU AGHEU"
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:1",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 1,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u00cen anul"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " al doilea al \u00eemp\u0103ratului Darius, \u00een ziua \u00eent\u00e2i a lunii a \u015fasea, cuv\u00e2ntul Domnului a vorbit prin prorocul Hagai c\u0103tre Zorobabel"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", fiul lui \u015eealtiel, dreg\u0103torul lui Iuda, \u015fi c\u0103tre Iosua"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "\u2020"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", fiul lui Io\u0163adac"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "\u2020\u2020"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", marele preot, astfel:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Ezra 4:24",
              "Ezra 5:1",
              "Zah 1:1"
            ],
            "**": [
              "1 Cron 3:17",
              "1 Cron 3:19",
              "Ezra 3:2",
              "Mat 1:12",
              "Luca 3:27"
            ],
            "\u2020": [
              "Ezra 3:2",
              "Ezra 5:2"
            ],
            "\u2020\u2020": [
              "1 Cron 6:15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:2",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 2,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u201eA\u015fa vorbe\u015fte Domnul o\u015ftirilor: \u2018Poporul acesta zice: \u00abN-a venit \u00eenc\u0103 vremea pentru zidirea din nou a Casei Domnului!\u00bb\u2019\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:3",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 3,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "De aceea cuv\u00e2ntul Domnului le-a vorbit prin prorocul Hagai"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " astfel:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Ezra 5:1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:4",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 4,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u201eDar"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " pentru voi a venit oare vremea s\u0103 locui\u0163i \u00een case c\u0103ptu\u015fite cu tavan, c\u00e2nd Casa aceasta este d\u0103r\u00e2mat\u0103?\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "2 Sam 7:2",
              "Ps 132:3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:5",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 5,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "A\u015fa vorbe\u015fte acum Domnul o\u015ftirilor: \u201eUita\u0163i-v\u0103"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " cu b\u0103gare de seam\u0103 la c\u0103ile voastre!"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Plang 3:40",
              "Hag 1:7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:6",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 6,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Sem\u0103na\u0163i"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " mult \u015fi str\u00e2nge\u0163i pu\u0163in; m\u00e2nca\u0163i \u015fi tot nu v\u0103 s\u0103tura\u0163i; be\u0163i \u015fi tot nu v\u0103 potoli\u0163i setea; v\u0103 \u00eembr\u0103ca\u0163i \u015fi tot nu v\u0103 este cald \u015fi cine c\u00e2\u015ftig\u0103"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " o simbrie o pune \u00eentr-o pung\u0103 spart\u0103!\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Deut 28:38",
              "Osea 4:10",
              "Mica 6:14",
              "Mica 6:15",
              "Hag 2:16"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Zah 8:10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:7",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 7,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "A\u015fa vorbe\u015fte Domnul o\u015ftirilor: \u201eUita\u0163i-v\u0103 cu b\u0103gare de seam\u0103 la c\u0103ile voastre!"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:8",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 8,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Sui\u0163i-v\u0103 pe munte, aduce\u0163i lemne \u015fi zidi\u0163i Casa! Eu M\u0103 voi bucura de lucrul acesta \u015fi voi fi prosl\u0103vit\u201d, zice Domnul."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:9",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 9,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u201eV\u0103 a\u015ftepta\u0163i"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " la mult, \u015fi iat\u0103 c\u0103 a\u0163i avut pu\u0163in; l-a\u0163i adus acas\u0103, dar Eu l-am suflat"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ". Pentru ce?\u201d, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor. \u201eDin pricina Casei Mele, care st\u0103 d\u0103r\u00e2mat\u0103, pe c\u00e2nd fiecare din voi alearg\u0103 pentru casa lui."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Hag 2:16"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Hag 2:17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:10",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 10,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "De aceea cerurile"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " nu v-au dat roua \u015fi p\u0103m\u00e2ntul nu \u015fi-a dat roadele."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Lev 26:19",
              "Deut 28:23",
              "1 Imp 8:35"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:11",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 11,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Am chemat"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " seceta peste \u0163ar\u0103, peste mun\u0163i, peste gr\u00e2u, peste must, peste untdelemn, peste tot ce poate aduce p\u0103m\u00e2ntul, peste oameni \u015fi peste vite \u015fi peste tot"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " lucrul m\u00e2inilor voastre.\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "1 Imp 17:1",
              "2 Imp 8:1"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Hag 2:17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:12",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 12,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Zorobabel"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", fiul lui \u015eealtiel, Iosua, fiul lui Io\u0163adac, marele preot, \u015fi toat\u0103 r\u0103m\u0103\u015fi\u0163a poporului au ascultat glasul Domnului Dumnezeului lor \u015fi cuvintele prorocului Hagai, fiindc\u0103 Domnul Dumnezeul lor \u00eel trimisese. \u015ei poporul s-a temut de Domnul."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Ezra 5:2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:13",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 13,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Hagai, trimisul Domnului, a zis poporului, dup\u0103 porunca Domnului: \u201eEu sunt"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " cu voi, zice Domnul.\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Mat 28:20",
              "Rom 8:31"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:14",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 14,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Domnul"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " a trezit duhul lui Zorobabel, fiul lui \u015eealtiel, dreg\u0103torul"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " lui Iuda, \u015fi duhul lui Iosua, fiul lui Io\u0163adac, marele preot, \u015fi duhul \u00eentregii r\u0103m\u0103\u015fi\u0163e a poporului. A\u015fa c\u0103 ei au venit"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "\u2020"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " \u015fi s-au pus pe lucru \u00een Casa Domnului o\u015ftirilor, Dumnezeul lor,"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "2 Cron 36:22",
              "Ezra 1:1"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Hag 2:21"
            ],
            "\u2020": [
              "Ezra 5:2",
              "Ezra 5:8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 1:15",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 15,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u00een ziua a dou\u0103zeci \u015fi patra a lunii a \u015fasea, \u00een anul al doilea al \u00eemp\u0103ratului Darius."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        }
      ],
      "notes": {}
    },
    {
      "name": "Hagai 2",
      "chapter": 2,
      "link": "https://biblia.resursecrestine.ro/hagai/2",
      "verses": [
        {
          "type": "title",
          "text": "Slava celui de-al doilea Templu"
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:1",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 1,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u00cen a dou\u0103zeci \u015fi una zi a lunii a \u015faptea, cuv\u00e2ntul Domnului a vorbit prin prorocul Hagai astfel:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:2",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 2,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u201eVorbe\u015fte lui Zorobabel, fiul lui \u015eealtiel, dreg\u0103torul lui Iuda, lui Iosua, fiul lui Io\u0163adac, marele preot, \u015fi r\u0103m\u0103\u015fi\u0163ei poporului \u015fi spune-le:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:3",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 3,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u2018Cine"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " a mai r\u0103mas \u00eentre voi din cei ce au v\u0103zut Casa aceasta \u00een slava ei dint\u00e2i? \u015ei cum o vede\u0163i acum? A\u015fa cum este, nu pare ea"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " ca o nimica \u00een ochii vo\u015ftri?"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Ezra 3:12"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Zah 4:10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:4",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 4,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Acum fii tare"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", Zorobabel!\u2019, zice Domnul. \u2018Fii tare \u015fi tu, Iosua, fiul lui Io\u0163adac, marele preot! Fii tare \u015fi tu, tot poporul din \u0163ar\u0103\u2019, zice Domnul, \u2018\u015fi lucra\u0163i! C\u0103ci Eu sunt cu voi\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Zah 8:9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:5",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 5,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u2018Eu r\u0103m\u00e2n"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " credincios leg\u0103m\u00e2ntului pe care l-am f\u0103cut cu voi c\u00e2nd a\u0163i ie\u015fit din Egipt \u015fi Duhul Meu este \u00een mijlocul vostru; nu v\u0103 teme\u0163i!\u2019"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Exod 29:45",
              "Exod 29:46",
              "Neem 9:20",
              "Isa 63:11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:6",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 6,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "C\u0103ci a\u015fa vorbe\u015fte Domnul o\u015ftirilor: \u2018\u00cenc\u0103"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " pu\u0163in\u0103 vreme \u015fi voi cl\u0103tina \u00eenc\u0103 o dat\u0103"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " cerurile \u015fi p\u0103m\u00e2ntul, marea \u015fi uscatul;"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Hag 2:21",
              "Evr 12:26"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Ioel 3:16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:7",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 7,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "voi cl\u0103tina toate neamurile; comorile"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " tuturor neamurilor vor veni \u015fi voi umple de slav\u0103 Casa aceasta\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Gen 49:10",
              "Mal 3:1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:8",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 8,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u2018Al Meu este argintul \u015fi al Meu este aurul\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor."
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:9",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 9,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u2018Slava acestei Case din urm\u0103 va fi mai mare"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " dec\u00e2t a celei dint\u00e2i\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor, \u2018\u015fi \u00een locul acesta voi da"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " pacea\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor.\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Ioan 1:14"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Ps 85:8",
              "Ps 85:9",
              "Luca 2:14",
              "Efes 2:14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "title",
          "text": "Binecuv\u00e2ntarea f\u0103g\u0103duit\u0103"
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:10",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 10,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u00cen a dou\u0103zeci \u015fi patra zi a lunii a noua, \u00een anul al doilea al lui Darius, cuv\u00e2ntul Domnului a vorbit prin prorocul Hagai astfel:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:11",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 11,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u201eA\u015fa vorbe\u015fte Domnul o\u015ftirilor: \u2018Pune preo\u0163ilor urm\u0103toarea \u00eentrebare"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " asupra Legii:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Lev 10:10",
              "Lev 10:11",
              "Deut 33:10",
              "Mal 2:7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:12",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 12,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u00abDac\u0103 poart\u0103 cineva \u00een poala hainei sale carne sfin\u0163it\u0103 \u015fi atinge cu haina lui p\u00e2ine, bucate fierte, vin, untdelemn sau o m\u00e2ncare oarecare, lucrurile acestea vor fi sfin\u0163ite?\u00bb\u2019\u201d Preo\u0163ii au r\u0103spuns: \u201eNu!\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:13",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 13,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u015ei Hagai a zis: \u201eDac\u0103 se atinge cineva spurcat prin atingerea de un trup mort"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", de toate aceste lucruri, vor fi ele spurcate oare?\u201d Preo\u0163ii au r\u0103spuns: \u201eVor fi spurcate.\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Num 19:11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:14",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 14,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Atunci, Hagai, lu\u00e2nd iar\u0103\u015fi cuv\u00e2ntul, a zis: \u201e\u2018Tot a\u015fa"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " este \u015fi poporul acesta, tot a\u015fa este \u015fi neamul acesta \u00eenaintea Mea\u2019, zice Domnul, \u2018a\u015fa sunt toate lucr\u0103rile m\u00e2inilor lor: ce-Mi aduc ei acolo ca jertf\u0103 este spurcat!"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Tit 1:15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:15",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 15,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Uita\u0163i-v\u0103 dar cu b\u0103gare de seam\u0103"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " la cele ce s-au \u00eent\u00e2mplat p\u00e2n\u0103 \u00een ziua de azi, p\u00e2n\u0103 s\u0103 se fi pus piatr\u0103 pe piatr\u0103 la Templul Domnului!"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Hag 1:5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:16",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 16,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Atunci c\u00e2nd veneau la o gr\u0103mad\u0103"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " de dou\u0103zeci de m\u0103suri, nu erau \u00een ea dec\u00e2t zece; c\u00e2nd veneau la teasc s\u0103 scoat\u0103 cincizeci de m\u0103suri, nu erau \u00een el dec\u00e2t dou\u0103zeci!"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Hag 1:6",
              "Hag 1:9",
              "Zah 8:10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:17",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 17,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "V-am lovit"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " cu rugin\u0103 \u00een gr\u00e2u \u015fi cu t\u0103ciune \u015fi cu grindin\u0103; am lovit tot lucrul m\u00e2inilor"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " voastre. \u015ei cu toate acestea"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "\u2020"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": ", tot nu v-a\u0163i \u00eentors la Mine\u2019, zice Domnul."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Deut 28:22",
              "1 Imp 8:37",
              "Amos 4:9",
              "Hag 1:9"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Hag 1:11"
            ],
            "\u2020": [
              "Ier 5:3",
              "Amos 4:6",
              "Amos 4:8-11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:18",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 18,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u2018Uita\u0163i-v\u0103 cu b\u0103gare de seam\u0103 la cele ce s-au petrecut p\u00e2n\u0103 \u00een ziua de azi, p\u00e2n\u0103 \u00een a dou\u0103zeci \u015fi patra zi a lunii a noua, din ziua"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " c\u00e2nd a fost \u00eentemeiat Templul Domnului, uita\u0163i-v\u0103 cu b\u0103gare de seam\u0103 la ele!"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Zah 8:9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:19",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 19,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Mai"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " era s\u0103m\u00e2n\u0163\u0103 \u00een gr\u00e2nare? Nici via, nici smochinul, nici rodiul, nici m\u0103slinul n-au mai adus nimic. Dar, din ziua aceasta, \u00cemi voi da binecuv\u00e2ntarea Mea.\u2019\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Zah 8:12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "title",
          "text": "Nimicirea vr\u0103jma\u015filor \u015fi \u00een\u0103l\u0163area lui Zorobabel"
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:20",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 20,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "Cuv\u00e2ntul Domnului a vorbit a doua oar\u0103 lui Hagai, \u00een a dou\u0103zeci \u015fi patra zi a lunii, astfel:"
            }
          ],
          "references": {}
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:21",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 21,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u201eVorbe\u015fte lui Zorobabel, dreg\u0103torul"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " lui Iuda, \u015fi spune: \u2018Voi"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " cl\u0103tina cerurile \u015fi p\u0103m\u00e2ntul;"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Hag 1:14"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Hag 2:6",
              "Hag 2:7",
              "Evr 12:26"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:22",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 22,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "voi r\u0103sturna scaunul de domnie al \u00eemp\u0103r\u0103\u0163iilor, voi nimici puterea \u00eemp\u0103r\u0103\u0163iilor neamurilor, voi r\u0103sturna"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " \u015fi carele de r\u0103zboi \u015fi pe cei ce se suie \u00een ele; caii \u015fi c\u0103l\u0103re\u0163ii lor vor fi"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " tr\u00e2nti\u0163i la p\u0103m\u00e2nt \u015fi unul va pieri ucis de sabia altuia."
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Dan 2:44",
              "Mat 24:7"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Mica 5:10",
              "Zah 4:6",
              "Zah 9:10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hagai 2:23",
          "type": "verse",
          "number": 23,
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": "\u00cen ziua aceea\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor, \u2018pe tine, Zorobabele, fiul lui \u015eealtiel, robul Meu\u2019, zice Domnul, \u2018te voi lua \u015fi te voi p\u0103stra"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "*"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " ca pe o pecete, c\u0103ci"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "text": "**"
            },
            {
              "type": "normal",
              "text": " Eu te-am ales\u2019, zice Domnul o\u015ftirilor.\u201d"
            }
          ],
          "references": {
            "*": [
              "Cant 8:6",
              "Ier 22:24"
            ],
            "**": [
              "Isa 42:1",
              "Isa 43:10"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "notes": {}
    }
  ]
